{{Refimprove|date=December 2015}} {{Infobox newspaper |name=[[Image:Tbjlogo.png]] |image=[[Image:Tbj5yearanniversary.gif|200px|that's Beijing]] |caption=''That's Beijing'''s 5th-year anniversary cover |type= |format= |foundation=2001 |publisher=China Intercontinental Press |language=[[English language|English]] |headquarters=[[Beijing]], People's Republic of China |ISSN=1672-8025 |website=[http://www.thatsmags.com/beijing thatsmags.com/beijing] }} '''''That's Beijing''''' is a monthly English language magazine, distributed throughout Beijing, with a focus on news, current events, culture, art, music, fashion, nightlife and dining in Beijing. It is owned by Shanghai-based publishing group, Urbanatomy Media, who also own, ''[[That's Shanghai]]'' and ''[[that's PRD]]'' (covering the Pearl River Delta). The China "That's" brand was started by Mark Kitto in 1998.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.prospectmagazine.co.uk/features/thatschina|title=That’s China!|work=Prospect Magazine}}</ref>
